00:00:33.524 --> 00:00:35.330
of the black civil rights movement

00:00:35.330 --> 00:00:37.388
in the United States.

00:00:37.388 --> 00:00:39.237
I was in California that night,

00:00:39.237 --> 00:00:41.123
which was ground zero at the time

00:00:41.123 --> 00:00:42.947
for another movement:

00:00:42.947 --> 00:00:45.940
the marriage equality movement.

00:00:45.940 --> 00:00:47.746
